&lt;p id="da5RpW"&gt;Admittedly, there aren’t &lt;em&gt;that&lt;/em&gt; many gadgets on sale yet — and we’ll likely start to see better deals trickle in as we get closer to the event — but we’ve still managed to dig up a few solid deals, particularly for those already embedded in the Amazon ecosystem. These include sizable discounts on the new &lt;a href="https://www.amazon.com/Echo-Hub/dp/B0BCR7M9KX?tag=theverge02-20" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;Echo Hub&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://www.amazon.com/release-Charcoal-bundle-Sengled-Smart/dp/B0CNWMCF1R?tag=theverge02-20" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;Amazon’s latest...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
